f dollars are spent, traded and earned in both the online advertising and crypto currency sectors every year.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Asimi was created as a value based utility token to&amp;nbsp; bridge the gap between these 2 power house markets by offering:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;A unique method of minting that allows anyone to earn Asimi from home&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A freely exchanged utility token for use within the online advertising industry&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Experience has told us that crypto currency is here to stay.&amp;nbsp; &lt;br /&gt;It has changed the way we use, move and earn money. &lt;br /&gt;We also see the increasing numbers of people that are looking online for ways to make money from home.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../uploadedimg/Asimi%20Tokens.png&quot; alt=&quot;Asimi tokens&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;483&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The ASIMI MISSION&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The mission for Asimi is the deliverence of a real and long standing business prodcut to help anyone reach their online goals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Let\'s empower individuals to embrace their entrepreneurial spirit and live life on their own terms. We as an international community harness the power of blockchain and open the doors to a new way of advertising and earning that ultimately offers people more choice in their life.&amp;rdquo; &lt;br /&gt;- Luke Millard / CEO&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To fufill this mission statement, Asimi is designed to;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;To break down the barriers of entry into home based business&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;To simplify a work from home income opportunity and allow anyone to earn online from day 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;To create an advertising portal designed to retain a qualified, captive viewing audience with quality advertising for online businesses&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&