(17, 'Hashing Ad Space Monthly Update.  News and Statistics For March 2021', 'Hashing Ad Space', 'Asimi minting, decentralized system, earn crypto, minting crypto, earn from home, earn for free, new decentralized system, hashing ad space, legacy company, no deposits, no withdrawals, earn online, news and updates for march, second asimi play game, exciting', 'News and updates released by Hashing Ad Space include the release of the second Asimi Play game, a new website design, excitement surrounding the decentralized Asimi Minting,  Asimi trading news, 	advertising statistics, and more.', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;It has been another great month at Hashing Ad Space!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Read below for a complete overview for the month of March!&amp;nbsp; It is an exciting time for Hashing Ad Space ae are on track to achieve many of the goals set out over two years ago!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;1. AsimiPlay: The 2nd Asimi Game has officially launched!&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;background-color: #ffffff;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://asimiplay.com/asimi-chess-champion&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://asimiplay.com/asimi-chess-champion&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1617226542309000&amp;amp;usg=AFQjCNH6TYlFMREYRkXSUmCVSZuM3aX08g&quot;&gt;Asimi Chess Champion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Players can play and win as many chess games as they like and become the champion, to collect Asimi!&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Asimi prizes to be won every month for the leaderboard board.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://ci4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/i69bu57WxGgQW7TP2BVI1Uogll3T54e_OoiyNFueAsgvNhLJPkMcYMfNBaPJpfRsLtdZGyoFYAm8YDnY9DleBAhOWcq7BpT9ZxkQ6if74-JEQ46yh88m4lphctdY39NyoenSMwdA4KePowKAy-JmAs10YBgeH3JmO-EUTw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://m.gr-cdn-4.com/getresponse-zrtR4/photos/75daa319-6a93-4f87-a5e4-66042dd48772.jpg?img1617139149501&quot; width=&quot;447&quot; height=&quot;339&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This state-of-the-art Chess AI forces players to push their knowledge to the limits while also learning new moves with helpful &quot;Suggest Move&quot; hints that teach by example and ultimately help players win, plus allows them to impress and beat their friends the next time they play!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Imagine playing Chess, gaining skills, and winning prizes! That\'s precisely what Asimi Chess Champion does. Asimi Chess Champion awards prizes to the top Chess players each month! Players can track their progress on the Chess&amp;nbsp;&lt;a title=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://asimiplay.com/blog/asimiplay-leaderboards-using-google-play-games-app.&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://asimiplay.com/blog/asimiplay-leaderboards-using-google-play-games-app.&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1617226542309000&amp;amp;usg=AFQjCNHo5nFzkmht_OIXIgQsnd7mnH5lqQ&quot;&gt;leaderboards&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and win real Asimi prizes just for having fun playing Chess!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;See all of the Games at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a title=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://asimiplay.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://asimiplay.com/&amp;am