nk&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.hashingadspace.com/about.php&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1617226542309000&amp;amp;usg=AFQjCNEEdm6q48yKzEMT0tPeo6DYKev5XA&quot;&gt;https://www.&lt;wbr /&gt;hashingadspace.com/about.php&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;5. Asimi Tokens&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Asimi was trading steadily around 6-7c USD for the past month.The new year has brought much higher trading activity.&amp;nbsp;The last 30 days&amp;nbsp;over 1 Million Asimi tokens exchanged hands&amp;nbsp;on the Waves exchange.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;See Waves Exchange and watch&amp;nbsp;&lt;a title=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://hashingadspace.funnelbundle.io/getting-started-guide/ow-to-buy-asimi-with-your-credit-card-copy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://hashingadspace.funnelbundle.io/getting-started-guide/ow-to-buy-asimi-with-your-credit-card-copy&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1617226542309000&amp;amp;usg=AFQjCNHS_cxiovF6wPrWsMpufj3WNtWs0Q&quot;&gt;this video&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to learn how to get Asimi.&lt;br /&gt;On top of that, over $600,000&amp;nbsp;worth of Asimi has been paid to members\' personal wallets in the last 3 months! &lt;strong&gt;Just&amp;nbsp;outstanding!&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You can be&amp;nbsp;one of those that are earning!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;6. Minting Earnings&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The top Asimi minting earners are still earning &lt;em&gt;hundreds of dollars&lt;/em&gt; worth of Asimi 