(20, 'Hashing Ad Space Monthly Update. News and Statistics For April 2021', 'Hashing Ad Space', 'Hashing Ad Space, Hashing ad Space Update, what is Hashing Ad Space.', 'News and updates for Hashing Ad Space include the featured ad, design update to advertiser section, continued growth surrounding the decentralized Asimi Minting, Asimi trading news, advertising statistics, and more.', '&lt;h2&gt;It has been another big month at Hashing Ad Space!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is a pleasure to have you with us in this exciting time for Hashing Ad Space as we continue to power forward toward our goals! Read the 15 point guide below for a complete overview for the month of April!&amp;nbsp; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. The successful launch of the Featured Ad!&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We added a&amp;nbsp;featured&amp;nbsp;ad&amp;nbsp;to Hashing&amp;nbsp;Ad&amp;nbsp;Space that&amp;nbsp;helps both advertisers and earners!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../uploadedimg/Featured%20ad%20earn%20dashboard.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;104&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It\'s now&amp;nbsp;easier than ever to &lt;strong&gt;earn&amp;nbsp;some quick crypto for free&lt;/strong&gt; with the&amp;nbsp;featured&amp;nbsp;ad!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each day&amp;nbsp;you will see the&amp;nbsp;top ad&amp;nbsp;displayed&amp;nbsp;as a notification on your members area. Click the &quot;Watch here&quot; link to view the&amp;nbsp;ad&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;instantly earn the displayed amount. Easy :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advertisers&lt;/strong&gt; now get more exposure to all members of Hashing Ad Space via the featured ad. The featured ad also displays the title of the ad to help grab attention and receive potentially thousands of views from interested people.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;To set up a featured ad and have your website seen, log in to the advertiser section to set up your V2E campaign and have your website featured at Hashing Ad Space!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;../advertiser/index.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.hashingadspace.com/advertiser/index.php&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1620261806228000&amp;amp;usg=AFQjCNGYb0AkI01TL7N7ylahQNx9w0rguQ&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;https://www.hashingadspace.&lt;wbr /&gt;com/advertiser/index.php&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;Read more about the featured ad and how to setup&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;../article/hashing-ad-space-has-added-a-new-featured-ad-for-the-benefit-of-both-crypto-earners-and-crypto-business-advertisers&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;2. We launched the 3rd AsimiPlay Game!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Yes! This game pays you to play and includes refer-a-friend bonuses!!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;text-widget-1619833807683&quot; data-type=&quot;TextWidget&quot; data-delay=&quot;&quot; data-animation-duration=&quot;&quot; data-animation-delay=&quot;&quot; data-animation=&quot;lazyAnimation-&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Colour Countdown! A progressively difficult colour combination game to race the clock and complete the combinations before running out of time! Complete the levels to earn in-game coins. Your coins are redeemable to real-world prizes..! Nice!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://asimiplay.com/colour-countdown&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://asimiplay.com/colour-countdown&quot;&gt;https://asimiplay.com/colour-countdown&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;For every successful level you pass, yes, you\'ll earn coins, but be careful, with each unsuccessful attempt, you lose a coin to restart the level! Damn... With time NOT on your side, do your best to pass the levels with every attempt as successful players can redeem the coins for&amp;nbsp;real prizes including, Amazon and Google Play gift cards and Asimi tokens!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../uploadedimg/Colour_Countdown-0015579.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;image-widget-1619888586036&quot; data-type=&quot;ImageWidget&quot; data-delay=&quot;&quot; data-animation-duration=&quot;&quot; data-animation-delay=&quot;&quot; data-animation=&quot;lazyAnimation-&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div data-slide=&quot;//content.app-sources.com/s/64360779643921142/uploads/Compressed/Colour_Countdown-0015579.png&quot;&gt;&lt;a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;3. New Asimi Minting system&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The new minting system is powering forward with another full month of decentralized payments working perfectly!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do you know we have paid over 500,000 Asimi tokens to minters this month alone? It is massive and there is plenty of Asimi for you to earn too!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Minters now getting paid directly to thier wallets is proving to be a BIG benefit for minters.&lt;br /&gt;Every day, minters earn Asimi to their wallet. If you haven\'t yet, be sure to get setup. (You only need to be the proud owner of 100 Asimi tokens to participate and get paid daily)&lt;br /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LEARN HOW TO SETUP ASIMI MINTING &lt;a href=&quot;../article/the-comprehensive-beginners-guide-to-minting-asimi-tokens&quot;&gt;HERE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://ci5.googleusercontent.com/proxy/p7EQejxzrt_CdYtYIGm2B63y9zC-VEpDTKA3-ofqlnklsdpUsUYDoT2XHFS4QCXsjWYOzZoYFu_xKnN0TkN9ESdnqiyu6Fmh60Pz-Mv9cpGXnYeXUDIBGbEBLe0w9LVFJmoqcImitTxWewwhxUz9be8jHSDo3fS7GSaaqw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://m.gr-cdn-4.com/getresponse-zrtR4/photos/6d6c6677-bccb-4348-856b-abc7f82fceec.png?img1617139149501&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;301&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;4. Surveys News&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The all-new 2nd survey system is working great!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This 2nd survey option is simple, fast, and available to more areas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;Surveys are a fantastic way to get a lot of Asimi fast!&lt;br /&gt;Get ready for SURVEY THURSDAY again this week!&lt;br /&gt;Earnings are highest on survey Thursday.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Anyone can get started earning by completing surveys just register an account&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hashingadspace.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;, or log in to earn, all for free :)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The global survey activity is growing! Congratulations to everyone earning by completing surveys this month!&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/pF0uuJY1Ru9Q3r-dZAlQfBEim14M3DlhB_qVTWveMnvd-TEF9TtAIwv4ymbWYX8cna6_QRQ9KpXf96o6r9yLrwwfv-j-Lwyecafv57AO4bWs_6kUwOkLbE8NdPjk3dCT2BNQpTMOBseDtGC62ZbXHuyVBi_RlOgzPxVzOQ=s0-d-e1-ft#https://m.gr-cdn-4.com/getresponse-zrtR4/photos/619885f8-585e-4d1b-9491-e25d8da37087.png?img1617139149501&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;259&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #262626; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #262626; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;5. New&amp;nbsp;Advertiser Members Page Designs&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We have added a new look to a variety of advertiser members\' area website pages this month. With the new look of home pages and the addition of simple&amp;nbsp;explainer videos last month,&amp;nbsp; now the advertiser section has been updated to match the new look. See the new pages by logging in here:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Advertise:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;../advertiser/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.hashingadspace.com/advertiser/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1617226542309000&amp;amp;usg=AFQjCNFgyV438K3njcbaBMcDhAkJdbqdNw&quot;&gt;https://www.&lt;wbr /&gt;hashingadspace.com/advertiser/&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;6. Free Advertiser Raffle!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Advertisers can now win advertising for FREE!&amp;nbsp;We have launched&amp;nbsp;our&amp;nbsp;NEW advertiser&amp;nbsp;raffle!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It\'s&amp;nbsp;free to enter&amp;nbsp;for your chance&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;win free advertising&amp;nbsp;at Hashing&amp;nbsp;Ad&amp;nbsp;Space&amp;nbsp;every day!!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;table style=&quot;font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0px;&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;m_7399439093530063945gr-mltext-qcmfji&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0px; padding: 10px; word-break: break